    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small boxes, typically of wood, designed for holding one or more packs of playing cards, and sometimes also accessories to card games such as gaming chips.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
